OL,3,CSarwar puts focus on islanders
OL,4,C'treated as afterthought' by current
OL,5,Cgovernments
OL,7,FScotland's island communities are
OL,8,F"treated as an afterthought" by both
OL,9,Fthe Scottish and UK governments, Anas
OL,10,FSarwar has said.
OL,12,FThe Scottish Labour leader claimed
OL,13,Fislanders have suffered as a result of
OL,14,Fthe "incompetent and dysfunctional"
OL,15,Fgovernments, as he highlighted how
OL,16,F"Tory economic turmoil" has led to
OL,17,Fprices for goods in remote areas often
OL,18,Fbeing higher than in other parts of
OL,19,Fthe UK.
