OL,4,C'treated as afterthought' by current
OL,5,Cgovernments
OL,7,FMr Sarwar also criticised the Scottish
OL,8,FGovernment for its failure to deliver
OL,9,Fnew ferries to run on lifeline routes,
OL,10,Fand he accused ministers of failing to
OL,11,Finvest in rural housing and healthcare.
OL,13,FAhead of an election campaign visit to
OL,14,Fthe Western Isles on Saturday, Mr
OL,15,FSarwar said: "For too long Scotland's
OL,16,Fislands and rural communities have
OL,17,Fbeen forced to pay the price for two
OL,18,Fincompetent and dysfunctional
OL,19,Fgovernments.
