OL,3,CSarwar puts focus on islanders
OL,4,C'treated as afterthought' by current
OL,5,Cgovernments
OL,7,F"Tory economic turmoil has hit these
OL,8,Fcommunities hard, pushing already-high
OL,9,Fenergy and food bills through the roof.
OL,11,F"Meanwhile, the SNP has piled on
OL,12,Fpressure as it presides over a ferry
OL,13,Ffiasco, a rural housing crisis and the
OL,14,Fdecline of rural healthcare.
OL,16,F"Rural communities and islands have
OL,17,Fseen public services hollowed out by
OL,18,Ftwo governments treating them as an
OL,19,Fafterthought."
