OL,7,FHe said Labour is "fighting to win in
OL,8,Fevery single part of Scotland" in the
OL,9,FGeneral Election on July 4, as he
OL,10,Fvowed the party will "deliver change
OL,11,Ffor every single part of Scotland".
OL,13,FMr Sarwar added: "Labour's plans to
OL,14,Fback 'Brand Scotland' will help to
OL,15,Funlock the vast economic potential of
OL,16,Frural Scotland and its iconic food,
OL,17,Fdrink and tourism industries.
